-kingdom-player-recreates-majoras-mask-alien-invasion-3473116">在这里</a>查看一下。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/zelda-64-developer-shares-trailer-with-restored-ocarina-of-time-content-3483933">《塞尔达 64》开发商分享的预告片中修复了《时之笛》的内容，该预告片</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
